Use case diagrams help visualize how users interact with the system. They show different actions users can perform and how the system responds. For the Predictive Stock Management System, use case diagrams were created to clearly understand user interactions.

Main Actors

Admin

Store Manager / User

System

Core Use Cases

Login to system

Add stock details

Update stock quantity

View inventory levels

Generate demand prediction

Receive low-stock alerts

View dashboard reports

Manage users (Admin)

These diagrams help simplify complex requirements into visual form. They also make it easier for stakeholders and developers to understand system behavior. Use case diagrams are included in the appendix of the SRS document.
